{"type":null,"faqId":46168,"title":"为什么拍照时摄像头发热？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.0625in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>为了追求卓越的拍照图像质量，荣耀7i增加了单反级别的图像处理芯片，这个芯片的耗电量相对较大 。摄像头模块体积有限，而且可以旋转，因此热量不会传递给机身，为了保证摄像模块坚实耐用，是全金属材质，金属材料使得热感受明显一点，这都是技术上的必然结果，不过无论是机身还是摄像模块，都有完备的温度控制和多重温度保护措施，远满足安全标准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1948","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376113000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":40,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"拍照,摄像头发热","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}